Jeremy Clarkson set to appear on Have I Got News For You on April 25 . 
  He was sacked from Top Gear on March 25 after punching producer Oisin Tymon over a steak dinner . 
  The TV host will appear as a guest presenter on the satirical panel show . 
  It is believed he was booked to host the show before he was sacked . 
  Clarkson was dropped from the BBC but is not banned from appearing on the BBC . 
  He will appear on the show on the day before he is due to return to Top Gear . 
 